These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-8-1::.
3 different games are played: go, canasta, billiard
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, water
3 different pets are kept: turtle, goldfish, bird
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, sunflower, iris
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, turquise, lavender
City: san-francisco, venice, new-york
 1. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
 2. the person who growsdahlia is not to the right of the owner of the bird##8
 3. the person playing billiard is not to the left of the owner of the goldfish##8
 4. the owner of the turtle is the person who likes lavender##1
 5. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##5
 6. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine##3
 7. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere to the right of the person who likes lavender##5
 8. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 9. the person drinking lemonade is somewhere to the left of the person playing billiard##5
10. the person traveling to venice is not to the left of the person who growssunflower##8
11. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left##1
12. the person who growsiris is not to the right of the person drinking lemonade##8
13. the person who growsiris is somewhere between the owner of the bird and the person playing go##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |
| Game          | go | canasta | billiard    |
| Beverage           | juice | lemonade   | water     |
| Pet   | turtle     | goldfish   | bird       |
| Flower   | sunflower    | iris   | dahlia     |
| Color   | lavender    | aquamarine   | turquise |
| City     | new-york     | san-francisco | venice     |

