 1. the colonial house is not to the right of the person playing scrabble##8
 2. the person drinking mirinda is the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the person playing scrabble is the cape-cod house##1
 4. the person driving the train is not to the left of the person playing scrabble##8
 5. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
 6. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 7. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 8. the person who likes light-blue is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking mirinda is not the colonial house##6
10. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the right of the person who likes light-blue##5
11. the person drinking mirinda is not to the right of the person drinking coffee##8
12. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching animation movies##5
13. the person watching animation movies is somewhere between the person driving the motorbike and the person who likes turquise##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |     3      |
